<p>In late 2024 Google Trends showed a <strong>400% spike</strong> in searches for “AI make money online.” What changed?</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Tools got stupid‑simple</strong>—no coding, just prompts.</li>
  <li><strong>Market demand</strong> for AI‑boosted services (copywriting, ad‑creative, store setups) is outpacing supply.</li>
  <li><strong>Remote first</strong>: brands don’t care where you live, only how fast you deliver.</li>
</ul>

<h2>7 Proven AI Side‑Hustles (Beginner Friendly)</h2>

<h3>1 • Done‑for‑You AI Shopify Stores</h3>
<p>Launch a fully‑branded one‑product store with AI‑generated copy, images and an upsell flow in <strong>48 hours</strong>. Charge $397–$997 per build.</p>

<h3>2 • Ad‑Creative Generator</h3>
<p>Use tools like <a href="https://durable.co" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Durable</a> and Midjourney to pump out high‑converting TikTok hooks in minutes.</p>

<h3>3 • AI Email Rescue Service</h3>
<p>Set up abandoned‑cart flows that recover 15–20% of lost revenue. Brands happily pay a % of recovered sales.</p>

