<h2>FAQs (People Also Ask)</h2>
<h3>Is AI side‑hustling saturated in 2025?</h3>
<p>No. Adoption is still <em>early</em>; brands know they need AI but lack in‑house expertise.</p>

<h3>How much time do I need per week?</h3>
<p>Most students spend 5–8 hours setting up, then 2 hours/week maintaining.</p>

<h3>Do I need to know code?</h3>
<p>Zero coding. The free tools in our toolkit handle prompts, design, even product photos.</p>

<h3>What’s the quickest way to land clients?</h3>
<p>Offer a results‑based trial: 10% of recovered revenue or first product launch free.</p>

